 * setting is enabled. Behind a reverse proxy / load balancer (Nginx, ELB,
 * Cloudflare, etc.), every request appears to come from the proxy's IP, so all
 * clients share one bucket. Enable trust proxy so Express reads the client IP
 * from X-Forwarded-For:
